{"tid":1124383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：香港金融服務優勢最能夠配合國家所需","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T08:20:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd10e0ff9c9813c864641e66adcaeabcb88c746","tid":1124383,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1454466_1_L_20190425113012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1454466_1_L_20190425113012.jpg&h=b8f77982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在北京出席一帶一路國際合作高峰論壇，她在主題論壇發言時說，香港於一帶一路倡議中扮演積極角色，認為本港作為國際金融中心，金融服務優勢，最能夠配合國家所需。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥致辭時又引述亞洲開發銀行數字，指由2016年至2030年，亞洲發展中國家需要1萬7千億美元的融資需求，反映一帶一路國家有龐大基建融資需求，亦需要私人市場的投資。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥認為，本港在一國兩制下，加上法治及符合國際水平的監管制度，以及龐大資本及債劵市場，亦是全球第二大人民幣離岸結算中心，具有將內地資本市場連接到世界的豐富經驗，相信香港可為一帶一路大型項目，提供金融服務及風險管理的一站式選擇。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454466-20190425.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454466-20190425.htm&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=3aeffe91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454466-20190425.htm&h=c79578a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454466-20190425.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1323abee062c33e2eb5b9f5f6935dac4261db6a1","tid":1124383,"uid":140302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"4000蚊都搞成咁 <br />\n<br />\n寡人笑撚咗"},{"pid":"f0ca6b553d687d3db3585b3e3272f103e2af3df7","tid":1124383,"uid":27038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"最能夠配合國家昆水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786cc06d0ad04ebcb652d6fbd7208